name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: FLUX AI image generator - flux.1 schnell/dev/pro by Black Forest Labs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Flux is an AI model for generating images from text prompts. It was developed by Black Forest Labs to produce high-quality images with a focus on photorealism and creative flexibility. This model aims to give users fine-grained control over image generation through an extensive set of customization options and modifiers.
